-- ADB to Lend $1 Billion to Philippines to Build Renewable Energy Projects
-- Cecilia Yap
-- 2010-06-23T03:34:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/adb-to-lend-1-billion-to-philippines-to-build-renewable-energy-projects.html

          
          
             The Asian Development Bank will lend
$1 billion to support renewable energy and energy efficiency
projects in the Philippines, its principal energy specialist
Sohail Hasnie told reporters today in Manila. This
will be in the form of loans and grants, Hasnie said.  
